{"tid":1117883,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「右鉤拳柴犬」憑殘影走紅還被實體化","createTime":"2019-04-21T04:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T10:57:49.000Z","uid":33359,"like":35,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c2825f09c949f01e9c671ae9e2814765a1828490","tid":1117883,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T04:29:36.000Z","msg":"「右鉤拳柴犬」憑殘影走紅還被實體化 網笑到崩潰：看懂就回不去惹<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.ettoday.net/images/4037/d4037761.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4037%2Fd4037761.jpg&h=eac98450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖／翻攝自推特／Ninjamaaaaaan）<br />\n<br />\n▲一張柴犬的殘影照，被二創到令人噴笑。（圖／翻攝自推特／Ninjamaaaaaan）<br />\n<br />\n寵物小組／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n日本推特每隔一陣子總能掀起新話題，繼「衝擊的育兒畫面」、「失敗的寵物照」系列爆紅之後，最近走紅的討論串莫過於這隻柴犬，不僅被各種KUSO，甚至還被做成實體化的公仔，非常爆笑。（即時接收毛毛軍團訊息！快加寵物雲Line）<br />\n<br />\n推主Ninjamaaaaaan在推特上傳自家柴犬的照片，好笑的是，柴柴正要轉身、卻因為相機只拍到殘影，結果就是這個看起來就像正在揮出一記右鉤拳的畫面。原本推主只是要分享自己拍到的失敗畫面，沒想到被其他網友畫上線條，柴柴的右鉤拳形象更深植人心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.ettoday.net/images/4037/d4037763.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4037%2Fd4037763.jpg&h=a8ec832d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／翻攝自推特／Ninjamaaaaaan）<br />\n<br />\n▲畫上線條之後，更有那麼一回事了！<br />\n<br />\n網友笑噴留言「原來是超壯的狗界阿諾啊！」「看懂之後就回不去了啦。」後來這張照片更是被無限上綱，P成各種二次創作，甚至不到4天就有人設計出實體公仔、T恤，右鉤拳柴犬的魅力還在猛爆式擴大中。（ETtoday寵物雲有IG了，快按追蹤）<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.ettoday.net/images/4037/d4037765.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4037%2Fd4037765.jpg&h=6e838aaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／翻攝自推特／Ninjamaaaaaan） <br />\n<br />\n▲還被做成實體化的公仔。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.ettoday.net/images/4037/d4037762.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4037%2Fd4037762.jpg&h=644683b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／翻攝自推特／Ninjamaaaaaan）<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.ettoday.net/images/4037/d4037758.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4037%2Fd4037758.jpg&h=cc0ba3be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／翻攝自推特／Ninjamaaaaaan）<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.ettoday.net/images/4037/d4037759.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4037%2Fd4037759.jpg&h=00a1a320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／翻攝自推特／Ninjamaaaaaan）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醬:<a href=\"https://pets.ettoday.net/news/1426453?from=fb_et_pets&amp;fbclid=IwAR3C-GEjNIa2lyCrj4RU-x-pvkRvfE5Wy6tlxbhCs_LfQDpuaQbN1lyI6Ys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpets.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1426453%3Ffrom%3Dfb_et_pets%26fbclid%3DIwAR3C-GEjNIa2lyCrj4RU-x-pvkRvfE5Wy6tlxbhCs_LfQDpuaQbN1lyI6Ys&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=faaf8268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pets.ettoday.net/news/1426453?from=fb_et_pets&amp;fbclid=IwAR3C-GEjNIa2lyCrj4RU-x-pvkRvfE5Wy6tlxbhCs_LfQDpuaQbN1lyI6Ys</a>"},{"pid":"f501dd9931e9c7f36e62c9d837f0e2fd4d6c4c98","tid":1117883,"uid":204803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640a6871796d446d92df333778b7cce19177b7d9","tid":1117883,"uid":146558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T04:41:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8c4ac08ba0d203a7b0f17829cb7dff1d28e431","tid":1117883,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T04:42:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想比佢屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"ecb3b0b6a0fb8a08e0bf2f691b2f3205ad3c2460","tid":1117883,"uid":33359,"like"